reactions.title: Uncanny Dodge
reactions.info:
Once per round, you can use your roguish experience to dodge half of the damage of an attack if you can see the attack coming towards you. Attacks with invisible weapons or when you are surprised can not be halved in this way.
If other effects would halve that damage, these halvings stack in an order logical with how they would occur: ie. 12 damage is dodged to 6 and then resistence (on your person) halves it to 3; OR 12 damage is reduced to 10 by a shield, then to 5 by your dodge.
